name: PvM Encyclopedia
description: Collection of high level guides compiled by high level players, including current record holders. Includes guides for every boss, and has breakdowns by skill level all the way up to extremely experienced.

name: AoD 7-10 Man
description: Aod 7-10 accepts all experience levels. By joining you will have access to their 7 man teams after verification of your member tag to them.

name: Achievement Help
description:
Achievement Help is your one-stop shop for anything that you can achieve in RuneScape!

We assist players of all levels and experience with setting and smashing goals. With specialised advice on the Max cape, Completionist cape, Master quest cape, and Trimmed completionist cape, you won't find another Discord server that will elevate your game like Achievement Help.

name: The Regiment
description: Join the server to keep up with Regicidal AKA Mod Lee! Stream notifications, events, awesome discussions and more!

name: EDTeams
description: Elite Dungeon Teams is a non-toxic, learner friendly discord for finding teams for all Elite Dungeons. Information, achievement and boss guides, and strategies are provided to assist users with their Elite Dungeon journey.

name: teachingrots
description: The #1 FC for filling Rise of the Six teams.

name: Solak
description: A community for the RuneScape boss Solak, inside the server you can find team-making channels for learner, casual and experienced teams. Dedicated vod review channel, guides and all round discussion of end-game PvM. The largest Solak community welcoming all players that want to learn, improve or find teams for Solak.

name: LSPVM247
description:
We are a Friend's Chat where you can get your daily Reaper kills, Marks of war, Kill counts, and drops from King Black Dragon up to bosses such as Vorago, Solak and AOD.
The FC hosts daily masses and Learner lessions to help people get their kills. Masses are done in FC with the Lootshare system and drops are lootshare keeps. If you're interested, feel free to join the discord and hang around in the FC.

name: Rockman
description: A friendly community Vorago discord. Here you can find teams, get help and learn Vorago. Intended for all levels of experience at the boss. Both learners and experienced PvMers alike are welcome to join and find teams. This discord is a convenient place to find both normal & hard mode teams.

name: Friendlybot Server
description:
The Discord server for the Friendlybot and friends of Friendliness.
Feel free to join! For an overview of Friendlybot's features, check out: https://friendliness.me/help

name: Archaeology
description: For everything relating to the up-and-coming skill release of Archaeology in RuneScape! Join to learn more about the skill and discuss with other members.

name: Rago PvM
description: Welcome to our community dedicated to everything Vorago related. This includes team creating of all sizes everyday and at any skill level, as well as learning events which are hosted weekly via our Server. Helping people improve is our main goal.

name: Sheety
description: Sheety is a Dynamic Rotation Builder for RS3 that's being constantly updated with new features and following the PvM meta.
